        <p>SE Ranking's rank tracking accuracy is the standout metric. <strong>94.3% match rate against AccuRanker in our 30-day benchmark</strong> — the highest accuracy we have measured in a sub-$100 SEO suite. Site Audit catches 120+ issues (vs Semrush's 140+). The keyword database covers 7B+ keywords across 230+ Google regional databases — smaller than Semrush but adequate for most agency use cases.</p>

